%SCRIPT XSHELXIN
%%
%%
%% Read in a the cell, symm and atoms from a shelx file.
%%
{R SHELX Script version by R. Cooper. Based on the fortran program SXTOCA by
{R R.O. Gould, The University of Edinburgh, March 1994.
%%
