{R CELL card processed.
%%
%% Space group is the next thing to look for.
%%
%           EXTRACT REWIND
{I Looking for TITL instruction.
%         EVALUATE SFILERR = TRUE
%         LOOP
%           ON ERROR TERMINATE
%           ON END TERMINATE
%           EXTRACT SHRIEK
%           CLEAR
%%           EXTRACT TRANSFER COMMAND
